{"tid":2259631,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"擴音器點揀","createTime":"2020-10-27T03:37:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T11:29:02.000Z","uid":59090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7d42b45498f4180ea75123209baf99282914988e","tid":2259631,"uid":59090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:37:53.000Z","msg":"是咁的 要幫人買擴音器<br />\n佢本身己經有隻amplifier toa a2030 ，<br />\n買左隻speaker jbl control X<br />\n<br />\n後尾裝機師傅話呢兩隻一齊用會燒<br />\n但係問番原因 佢講左十幾分鐘都唔係好聽得明<br />\n<br />\n想請教一下 唔考慮國產牌子既話 <br />\n有咩平平地又好用既amplifier 匹配 jbl control X <br />\n又唔會燒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\njbl control x <br />\n頻率:\t90Hz ～ 20kHz<br />\n輸入功率:\t20W-100W<br />\n靈敏度:\t87dB<br />\n阻抗:\t8&Omega;<br />\n<br />\ntoa a2030<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.toa.jp/products/amplifiers/a-2000series/a-2030_ce-au.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.toa.jp%2Fproducts%2Famplifiers%2Fa-2000series%2Fa-2030_ce-au.html&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETeIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=a809dc09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.toa.jp/products/amplifiers/a-2000series/a-2030_ce-au.html</a>"},{"pid":"078fb4fbc1f0265dd32502a39ee30a267e3e9848","tid":2259631,"uid":59090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:51:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8259ef7ea913993d2af531ae719a19de474db1dd","tid":2259631,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:53:19.000Z","msg":"你個2030以卡拉OK多過以AMP， 30W未必推得郁JBL"},{"pid":"6dfbcff925384f2e27abd78b5aa25bc0303c9d69","tid":2259631,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:55:37.000Z","msg":"btw為左對JBL買部AMP又好似唔係好值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d26de07fe649959b8d33d5052dde06b0e2856f","tid":2259631,"uid":59090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8259ef7ea913993d2af531ae719a19de474db1dd","tid":2259631,"uid":4